<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>vim on Simba 的喵窩</title><link>https://blog.simbafs.cc/post/linux/vim/</link><description>Recent content in vim on Simba 的喵窩</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>en-us</language><lastBuildDate>Fri, 18 Aug 2023 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://blog.simbafs.cc/post/linux/vim/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Firenvim</title><link>https://blog.simbafs.cc/p/linux/vim/firenvim/</link><pubDate>Fri, 18 Aug 2023 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://blog.simbafs.cc/p/linux/vim/firenvim/</guid><description>&lt;img src="https://blog.simbafs.cc/og/linux/vim/firenvim.png" alt="Featured image of post Firenvim" />&lt;h1 id="firenvim">Firenvim&lt;/h1>
&lt;p>&lt;a class="link" href="https://github.com/glacambre/firenvim" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>firenvim&lt;/a> 是一個可以把 nvim 嵌入瀏覽器的插件，像是這樣&lt;br>
&lt;img src="https://blog.simbafs.cc/images/firenvim_in_leetcode.png"
